      • manualDrive

        public void manualDrive(double outputMagnitude,
                        double curve)
        Manually drive robot with output and curve
        Parameters:
        outputMagnitude - The speed setting for the outside wheel in a turn, forward or backwards, +1 to -1.
        curve - The rate of turn, constant for different forward speeds. Set curve < 0 for left turn or curve > 0 for right turn. Set curve = e^(-r/w) to get a turn radius r for wheelbase w of your robot. Conversely, turn radius r = -ln(curve)*w for a given value of curve and wheelbase w.
